{"tid":1053391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東亞17間分行電腦癱瘓 發言人︰受影響遍全港 暫未知起因","createTime":"2019-03-09T04:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T13:10:13.000Z","uid":36494,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e4e72160acd3b7adc9d91852acb6202ac1e74c91","tid":1053391,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T04:30:04.000Z","msg":"東亞銀行今早出現電腦系統故障，根據東亞銀行網頁顯示，由於網絡不穩定，銀行部份分行未能提供櫃位服務，銀行建議客戶如需進行銀行交易，可暫時使用網上或手機銀行服務，以及自動櫃員機服務。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果向東亞銀行發言人查詢，對方表示目前系統正在搶修，希望盡快恢復服務。她指受影響的分行數目為17間，分佈於香港、九龍及新界，現時正調查事故起因，但「要等前線救咗火先」。她表示今次只是櫃台服務有影響，所有網上銀行及櫃員機等服務都能正常使用。"},{"pid":"2acde16c96766a1c783800cbeda6da84fd079ffa","tid":1053391,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T04:30:48.000Z","msg":"東亞真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f762c8d4dda0c83237474ddac8033d93748f3da3","tid":1053391,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T04:31:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"240f60d8984d8c5277731be3629c0d63525a909a","tid":1053391,"uid":61954,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T04:31:34.000Z","msg":"又有IT狗俾人炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d938e959f03a13c3bb8c5191763031ff707f63bd","tid":1053391,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2acde16c96766a1c783800cbeda6da84fd079ffa","tid":1053391,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T04:30:48.000Z","msg":"東亞真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T04:33:18.000Z","msg":"病夫銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6d88804f465b015d6fe6950a9e72e2e4c31f61","tid":1053391,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"240f60d8984d8c527773